I’m really excited to announce that I have some prints now being sold through Inventaire including this image, ‘Shinjuku Crossing’. It's the first part of a Tokyo Diptych: Shinjuku/Shibuya.

Inventaire is a fantastic new shop in Paris selling artists prints. Some of my favourite illustrators are involved. A real pleasure to be involved.

Go to  @inventaireparis for more info

From 70€.
Only avalaible at Inventaire - 54 rue Beaubourg, Paris 3. 
Soon on www.inventaireparis.com
